&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, AI, ML, or a related technical field, or equivalent practical experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrable expertise and hands-on experience in Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning, with deep knowledge in at least one specific AI domain (e.g., NLP, LLMs, Speech Recognition).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience (typically 3+ years) designing, building, and evaluating AI/ML models and systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong programming skills, particularly in Python and familiarity with common ML libraries/frameworks (e.g., PyTorch, TensorFlow, scikit-learn, Hugging Face).&lt;/li&gt;
