&lt;p&gt;Bandwidth is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Director of AI Strategic Partnerships &amp;amp; Data Licensing&lt;/strong&gt; to lead our entry into the Generative AI and Large Language Model (LLM) ecosystem. Reporting directly to the Chief Strategy Officer (CSO), this is a high-impact, &quot;frontier&quot; role responsible for establishing Bandwidth as the essential voice layer for the world’s most sophisticated AI companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Unlike a traditional sales role, your success will be measured by the breadth and depth of formalized partnerships you secure with major AI players. You will be the bridge between Bandwidth’s global network and the next generation of AI-driven voice applications, while simultaneously architecting our first-ever voice data licensing program.&lt;/p&gt;
